            "body": "<p>The regex is <\/p>\n\n<pre><code>((http:\\/\\/|https:\\/\\/)?(www.)?(([a-zA-Z0-9-]){2,}\\.){1,4}([a-zA-Z]){2,6}(\\/([a-zA-Z-_\\/\\.0-9#:?=&amp;;,]*)?)?)\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/23695773/how-to-check-if-string-contain-the-url-or-link-and-retrieve-it\">Check this link for more information<\/a><\/p>\n",
