            "body": "<p>You could split the string on spaces and then test each 'word' in the resultant array using one of the methods in <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/11007008/whats-the-best-way-to-check-if-a-string-contains-a-url-in-java-android\">the answer you linked to above<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>String[] words = str.split(\" \");\nfor (String word : words) {\n    // test here using your favourite methods from the linked answer\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
