            "creation_date": 1449495826,
            "body": "<p>The easiest way is to use indexOf method. Like:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>String target =\" test http://www.test1.com\";\nString http = \"http:\";\nSystem.out.println(target.indexOf(http));\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Or, you can use Regular Expressions:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>String target =\"test http://www.test1.com\";\nString http = \"((http:\\\\/\\\\/|https:\\\\/\\\\/)?(www.)?(([a-zA-Z0-9-]){2,}\\\\.){1,4}([a-zA-Z]){2,6}(\\\\/([a-zA-Z-_\\\\/\\\\.0-9#:?=&amp;;,]*)?)?)\";\nPattern pattern = Pattern.compile(http);\nMatcher matcher = pattern.matcher(target);\nwhile (matcher.find()) {\n    System.out.println(matcher.start() + \" : \" + matcher.end());\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
